title: Wholesale Price of Woodpulp (Mechanical, No. 1, Domestic and Canadian, Delivered Consumer Mill) for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)-- Original Data, 1913-1942 (2)--Original Data, 1942-1958. Represents Delivered Price 1942 And After (Code 749.1), Quoted Weekly"Domestic And Canadian (Ranges)." No Change In Specifications After 1951, When New Bls Index Was First Published (New Code #09-10-31). Series Is Considered As Continuous. Source: Bls Wholesale Price Bulletin, Nos. 718, 736, 759, 785, 870, 877, 920, 947, 973, 1007, 1083, 1143, (For 1942-1951) And 1214 (For 1954-1956); Monthly Issues Of Bls, "Wholesale Prices And Price Indexes" (For 1952-1953, 1957, And 1958).

This NBER data series m04124b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
